<h6 class="kicker"><a href="//dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/legal/">LEGAL/REGULATORY Â»</a></h6>
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Federal Reserve Sees Slower Growth but Maintains Plans to Trim Stimulus <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> The Federal Reserve will reduce its monthly bond purchases by $10 billion a month and still expects to stop expanding its holdings this year, The New York Times writes. <span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/06/19/business/economy/fed-sees-slower-growth-but-maintains-plans-to-trim-stimulus.html?ref=business"> NEW YORK TIMES </a></span></p>
